               - generic:\n                      - combobox \"难度\" [ref=f2e240]\n                      - generic [ref=f2e241]: 中等\n              - button \"生成编程题\" [ref=f2e246] [cursor=pointer]\n            - article [ref=f2e552]:\n              - generic [ref=f2e553]:\n                - generic [ref=f2e554]: 编程题\n                - generic [ref=f2e556]: 基础\n                - generic [ref=f2e558]: 2 秒\n              - heading \"循环左移数组\" [level=3] [ref=f2e560]\n              - paragraph [ref=f2e561]: 给定一个包含n个整数的数组，将其循环左移一位后输出。\n              - heading \"输入格式\" [level=4] [ref=f2e562]\n              - paragraph [ref=f2e563]: 第一行一个整数n（1 ≤ n ≤ 1000），表示数组长度。 第二行n个整数，用空格分隔，表示数组元素。\n              - heading \"输出格式\" [level=4] [ref=f2e564]\n              - paragraph [ref=f2e565]: 一行，包含n个整数，表示循环左移一位后的数组，用空格分隔，末尾有换行。\n              - heading \"约束\" [level=4] [ref=f2e566]\n              - paragraph [ref=f2e567]: 1 ≤ n ≤ 1000; 每个数组元素的绝对值 ≤ 10000。\n              - heading \"样例\" [level=4] [ref=f2e568]\n              - article [ref=f2e569]:\n                - strong [ref=f2e570]: 输入\n                - generic [ref=f2e571]: 5 1 2 3 4 5\n                - strong [ref=f2e572]: 输出\n                - generic [ref=f2e573]: 2 3 4 5 1\n              - generic [ref=f2e574]:\n                - generic [ref=f2e575]: 编程语言\n                - radiogroup \"编程语言\" [ref=f2e577]:\n                  - generic [ref=f2e578]:\n                    - radio \"C++\" [checked] [ref=f2e579]\n                    - generic [ref=f2e580] [cursor=pointer]: C++\n                  - generic [ref=f2e581]:\n                    - radio \"C\" [ref=f2e582]\n                    - generic [ref=f2e583] [cursor=pointer]: C\n                  - generic [ref=f2e584]:\n                    - radio \"Python\" [ref=f2e585]\n                    - generic [ref=f2e586] [cursor=pointer]: Python\n              - textbox [ref=f2e588]: \"#include <iostream> using namespace std; int main() { long long a, b; cin >> a >> b; cout << a + b << '\\\\n'; return 0; }\"\n              - button \"运行并判题\" [ref=f2e590] [cursor=pointer]\n          - complementary [ref=f2e259]:\n            - generic [ref=f2e260]:\n              - generic [ref=f2e261]: 本次题目\n              - button \"循环左移数组 基础\" [ref=f2e592] [cursor=pointer]:\n                - strong [ref=f2e593]: 循环左移数组\n                - generic [ref=f2e594]: 基础\n  - button [ref=f2e283] [cursor=pointer]"}}
